{"_header": true, "schema": "hexa-lang/roadmap/2", "name": "hexa-lang.tools", "mk": 2, "perspective": "peer", "perspective_note": "tool peer (tool/ + tool/pkg + tool/bench + tool/diagnostics + tool/build) — 310+ tool entries 측 SSOT 측 fragmented. catalog + selftest matrix 측 부재. .roadmap.hexa-lang.excludes={sdk} 측 별개 측 internal devtool peer.", "goal": "tool/ 측 310 entries 측 catalog + per-tool selftest status + 측 ownership map + tool/pkg distribution channel 측 audit.", "required_conditions": ["RC1: tool/*.hexa (top-level ~290 entries) 측 catalog (name/role/owner/last-touched)", "RC2: 측 tool/_init/* + tool/_bench_runner_selftest_fixtures + tool/_spec_runner_selftest_fixtures 측 self-validation 측 audit", "RC3: tool/pkg/packages 측 distribution status (additive)"], "blockers": ["TL1: 310 entries 측 manifest 측 부재 — catalog 측 source-of-truth 측 디렉토리 자체 only", "TL2: tool/_emergency 측 위험도 명시 미수행 — emergency tool 측 lifecycle/owner audit", "TL3: tool/training 측 deploy 측 single dir 측 ownership/scope 측 doc 부재"], "cross_link": [".roadmap.hexa-lang"], "status": "PROPOSED_PEER_SCAFFOLD", "since": "2026-05-02"}
