{"id": "TL2", "kind": "audit", "title": "tool/_emergency 측 lifecycle policy", "rationale": "tool/_emergency 측 2 entries 측 위험도/ownership 측 doc 부재. emergency 도구 측 회수 정책 측 명시 필요.", "weakest_link": "no lifecycle doc", "status": "PROPOSED", "suggest_action": "tool/_emergency/README.ai.md 측 추가 — owner + activate-condition + revoke-trigger (additive only)"}
